mention\"><span class=\"mentions-prefix\">@</span>wolforg</a> va publier une proposition de changement de traduction afin de pr√©parer les discussions prochaines sur ce changement potentiel.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Traduction de ¬´¬†Downgrade¬†¬ª</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Deux termes ont √©t√© propos√©s¬†:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>R√©gression</li>\n<li>R√©trograder</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"has-black-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color has-text-color has-background\">Le terme choisi par l‚Äô√©quipe pour traduire ¬´¬†To downgrade¬†¬ª est ¬´¬†R√©trograder¬†¬ª.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\">\n<p>Fin de la r√©union √† 13h.<br>Prochaine r√©union pr√©vue le mardi 4 ao√ªt 2020.</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpfr/~4/Ao3PZzboq5c\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://fr.wordpress.org/team/2020/07/07/compte-rendu-de-la-35eme-reunion-du-6-juillet-2020/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"\n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		        \n		    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:4:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Child Theme Copy Settings\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpfr/~3/ZSA_ctpHPUg/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.echodesplugins.li-an.fr/plugins/child-theme-copy-settings/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0: